metadata.name: ROCAS Azules
metadata.description:
I express my interest for the natural world, which I define as the physical and material world that remains in its original state without the intervention of human beings, as opposed to their artificial world.
From this concept, I study the living nature and the way in which humans, surrealistically, could introduce themselves in it to achieve a subject-subject relationship.
Stones balance body and mind
Mixed Media on pure linen
83x52 inches
2023
